ector)|Sukumar]]\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"Sify\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/arya-2-releases-on-friday-premiere-today-news-telugu-kkfrnfbiiehsi.html|title=Arya -2 releases on Friday, Premiere today!|publisher=Sify|date=26 November 2009|accessdate=14 March 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150314165422/http://www.sify.com/movies/arya-2-releases-on-friday-premiere-today-news-telugu-kkfrnfbiiehsi.html|archivedate=14 March 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2010\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Varudu]]''\n| [[Bhanu Sri Mehra]]\n| Sandeep / Sandy\n| [[Gunasekhar]]\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/boxoffice.php?id=14936919&cid=2363|title=Arya, paid Rs 2 crore to play villain?|publisher=Sify|date=31 March 2010|accessdate=14 March 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150314165419/http://www.sify.com/movies/boxoffice.php?id=14936919&cid=2363|archivedate=14 March 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Vedam (film)|Vedam]]''\n| [[Anushka Shetty]]\n| Anand Raj / Cable Raju\n| [[Krish (director)|Krish]]\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"sify.com\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/allu-arjun-eyes-the-kollywood-market-news-telugu-kkfq3Iihehasi.html|title=Allu Arjun eyes the Kollywood market|publisher=Sify|date=30 May 2010|accessdate=14 March 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150314165418/http://www.sify.com/movies/allu-arjun-eyes-the-kollywood-market-news-telugu-kkfq3Iihehasi.html|archivedate=14 March 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2011\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Badrinath (film)|Badrinath]]''\n| [[Tamannaah]]\n| Badrinath\n| [[V. V. Vinayak]]\n| \n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"Badri\"/>\n|-\n| 2012\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Julayi]]''\n| [[Ileana D'Cruz]]\n| Ravindra \"Ravi\" Narayan\n| [[Trivikram Srinivas]]\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Allu-Arjuns-Julayi-rel