tor - Telugu]] - [[Vedam (film)|Vedam]] (2010)<ref>http://www.bollywoodlife.com/south-gossip/58th-filmfare-awards-2010-south-winners-list/</ref>\n*[[Filmfare Award for Best Actor - Telugu|Best Actor - Telugu]] - [[Race Gurram]] (2014) <ref>https://www.filmfare.com/news/winners-of-62nd-britannia-filmfare-awards-south-9643.html</ref>\n*[[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actor - Telugu|Best Supporting Actor - Telugu]] - [[Rudhramadevi (film)|Rudhramadevi]] (2015) <ref>https://www.filmfare.com/news/winners-of-the-63rd-britannia-filmfare-awards-south-13996.html</ref>\n*[[Filmfare Critics Award for Best Actor \u2013 South|Best Actor - Critics]] - [[Sarrainodu]] (2016) <ref>https://www.filmfare.com/news/winners-of-the-64th-jio-filmfare-awards-south-21594.html</ref>\n;[[Nandi Awards]]\n*[[Nandi Special Jury Award|Special Jury Award]] - [[Arya (2004 film)|Arya]] (2004)<ref>http://www.idlebrain.com/news/2000march20/nandiawards2004.html</ref>\n*[[Nandi Special Jury Award|Special Jury Award]] - [[Parugu]] (2008)<ref>http://www.idlebrain.com/news/2000march20/nandiawards2008.html</ref>\n*[[Nandi Award for Best Character Actor|Best Character Actor]] - [[Rudhramadevi (film)|Rudhramadevi]] (2015)<ref>https://www.chitramala.in/nandi-awards-winners-list-2014-2015-2016-255062.html</ref>\n;[[CineMAA Awards]]\n*[[CineMAA Awards|Best Male Debut]] - [[Gangotri (2003 film)|Gangotri]] (2003)\n*[[CineMAA Awards|Best Actor]] - [[Race Gurram]] (2014)<ref>http://english.tupaki.com/movienews/article/Cinemaa-Awards-Winners-list/30456</ref>\n*[[CineMAA Awards|Best Actor Jury]] - [[Rudhramadevi (film)|Rudhramadevi]] (2015) <ref>http://english.tupaki.com/movienews/article/Cinemaa-awards-2016-Winners-List/41198</ref>\n;[[South Indian International Movie Awards|SIIMA Awards]]\n*[[South Indian International Movie Awards|Stylish Youth Icon of South Indian Cinema (male)]] \u2013 Allu Arjun (2014)\n*[[South Indian International Movie Awards|Best Actor Critics choice]] - [[Rudhramadevi (film)|Rudhramadevi