cs.com/news/2016/4/4/mens-basketball-john-mclendon-elected-to-basketball-hall-of-fame-for-second-time.aspx |title=University of Kansas Athletics - John McLendon Elected to Basketball Hall of Fame for Second Time |publisher=Kuathletics.com |date= |accessdate=March 17, 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Ralph Miller]], former basketball and football player, enshrined as a coach\n* [[James Naismith]], former coach, enshrined as the inventor of basketball\n* [[Ernie Quigley]], former player, enshrined as a referee\n* [[Adolph Rupp]], former player, enshrined as a coach\n* [[Dean Smith]], former player, enshrined as a coach\n\n===Olympians===\n''Representing the [[United States men's national basketball team]] unless otherwise noted.''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Player\n!Medal\n|-\n| 1952 || [[Phog Allen]] (assistant coach) || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1952 || [[Charlie Hoag]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1952 || [[Bill Hougland]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1952 || [[John Keller]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1952 || [[Dean Kelley]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1952 || [[Bob Kenney]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1952 || [[Bill Lienhard]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1952 || [[Clyde Lovellette]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1956 || [[Bill Hougland]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1960 || [[Allen Kelley]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1968 || [[Jo Jo White]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Gold medal icon.svg]]\n|-\n| 1980 || [[Darnell Valentine]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| <nowiki>*</nowiki>\n|-\n| 1988 || [[Danny Manning]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Bronze meda