 Clippers]]\n* [[Markieff Morris]] \u2013 [[Los Angeles Lakers]]\n* [[Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk]] \u2013 Detroit Pistons\n* [[Kelly Oubre Jr.]] \u2013 Phoenix Suns\n<!-- Do not add Billy Preston. He never played a regular season game for Kansas and should not be included -->\n* [[Andrew Wiggins]] \u2014 [[Golden State Warriors]]\n\n<!-- ====Recently became a Free agent====\nThis section is former Jayhawks that were on an NBA roster during the 2018-2019 NBA season but are not on an NBA roster. Any players on this list that are not on a roster by the start of the season should be moved to former players -->\n\n====Two-way players====\nNBA teams can sign players to two\u2013way contracts allowing them to easily transition back and forth from the NBA team and their G\u2013League affiliate based on the needs of the team.\n\n* [[Frank Mason III]] \u2013 [[Milwaukee Bucks]] / [[Wisconsin Herd]]\n\n====Jayhawks in the NBA G-League====\nBelow are former Jayhawks under contract with a G-League team but are not on a two-way contract with an NBA team or under contract with an NBA team but on assignment to the G-League.\n\n* [[Malik Newman]] \u2014 [[Canton Charge]]\n* [[Wayne Selden Jr.]] \u2013 [[South Bay Lakers]]\n* [[Kevin Young (basketball, born 1990)|Kevin Young]] \u2013 [[Stockton Kings]]\n\n====Former players====\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-5}}\n* [[Cole Aldrich]] (2010\u201318)\n* [[Darrell Arthur]] (2008\u201318)\n* [[Charles B. Black]] (1948\u201351)\n* [[Tarik Black]] (2014\u201318)\n* [[Roger Bohnenstiel]] (1966\u201368)\n* [[B. H. Born]] (1952\u201354)\n* [[Bill Bridges (basketball)|Bill Bridges]] (1962\u201374)\n* [[Walter Roger Brown]] (1972\u201379)\n* [[Rick Calloway]] (1990)\n* [[Randolph Carroll]] (1978\u201379)\n* [[Mario Chalmers]] (2008\u201318)\n* [[Wilt Chamberlain]] (1959\u201372)\n* [[Eric Chenowith]] (1998\u201301)\n* [[Sherron Collins]] (2010\u201311)\n* [[Nick Collison]] (2003\u20132018)\n* [[Norm Cook]] (1976\u201377)\n* John Crawford (1978\u201381)\n* [[John D. Douglas]] (1977\u201378)\n* [[Greg Dreiling]] (1986\u201396)\n* [[Nolen Ellison]] (1961\u201363)\n* [[Jack Eskridge]] (1948)\n{{col-5}}\n* [[Ron Franz]] (1967\u201372)\n* [[Drew Gooden]] (2002\u201316)\n* [[Leonard Gray]] (1974\u201376)\n* [[Tony Guy]] (1979\u201382)\n* [[Darrin Hancock]] (1994\u201396)\n* [[Carl Henry (basketball)|Carl Henry]] (1983\u201384)\n* [[Xavier Henry]] (2010\u201314)\n* [[Wayne Hightower]] (1962\u201371)\n* [[Kirk Hinrich]] (2003\u201316)\n* [[Art Housey]] (1980\u201381)\n* [[Cedric Hunter]] (1991)\n* [[Darnell Jackson]] (2008\u201311)\n* [[Adonis Jordan]] (1993\u201398)\n* [[Sasha Kaun]] (2015\u20132016)\n* [[Allen Kelley]] (1953\u201354)\n* [[Dean Kelley]] (1951\u201353)\n{{col-5}}\n* [[Ron Kellogg]] (1983\u201386)\n* [[Maury King]] (1959\u201362)\n* [[Ken Koenigs]] (1975\u201378)\n* [[Raef LaFrentz]] (1998\u201309)\n* [[Keith Langford]] (2007\u201308)\n* [[Riney Lochmann]] (1967\u201369)\n* [[Ron Loneski]] (1957\u201359)\n* [[Al Lopes]] (1965\u201366)\n* [[Clyde Lovellette]] (1953\u201363)\n* [[Dave Magley]] (1982)\n* [[Danny Manning]] (1988\u201302)\n* [[Brian Martin (basketball)|Brian Martin]] (1985)\n* [[Aaron Miles (basketball)|Aaron Miles]] (2005)\n* [[Paul Mokeski]] (1979\u201390)\n* [[Roger Morningstar]] (1974\u201375)\n{{col-5}}\n* [[Dave Nash]] (1968\u201369)\n* [[Herb Nobles]] (1976\u201377)\n* [[Bob O'Brien]] (1947\u201348)\n* [[Greg Ostertag]] (1995\u201305)\n* [[Paul Pierce]] (1998\u20132017)\n* [[Scot Pollard]] (1997\u201308)\n* [[Kevin Pritchard]] (1990\u201395)\n* [[Mark Randall (basketball)|Mark Randall]] (1991\u201394)\n* [[Gil Reich]] (1953)\n* [[Ryan Robertson]] (1999)\n* [[Dave Robisch]] (1971\u201383)\n* [[Thomas Robinson (basketball)|Thomas Robinson]] (2012\u20132017)\n* [[Giff Roux]] (1946\u201348)\n* [[Brandon Rush]] (2008\u20132017)\n* [[Pierre Russell]] (1971\u201372)\n* [[Otto Schnellbacher]] (1948)\n* [[Josh Selby]] (2011\u201313)\n* [[Wayne Simien]] (2005\u201307)\n* [[Bruce Sloan]] (1967\u201369)\n* 